    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UISeries

    public abstract class AbstractChartSeries
extends javax.faces.component.UIComponentBase
    The <rich:chartSeries> defines the data to be plotted in a chart. It represents the set of values with a common label. Data can be passed using attribute data. It expects ChartDataModel object. You can also use facelet iteration.
    Author:
    Lukas Macko
